                <strong>Important:</strong> Cover Your Tracks is operated by the EFF — an independent digital rights nonprofit. It is not affiliated with Bloqr. We have no access to any data collected or displayed there, and we never will. We're linking to it because it's the best demonstration of fingerprinting that exists, run by people whose entire mission is protecting you.
              </p>
              <a href="https://coveryourtracks.eff.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="fp-test-link">
                Test your fingerprint at the EFF ↗
                <span class="fp-test-badge">Not our site. Not our data. Just a good tool.</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fp-bloqr-box">
          <div class="fp-bloqr-icon">🚧</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Anti-fingerprinting is coming in Bloqr v2.</h3>
            <p>
